msgid ""
"Export Prometheus metrics on webServer /metrics API. It only takes effect "
"when web server port is set."
msgstr ""
"在 webServer /metrics API 上匯出 Prometheus 指標。僅在設定 Web 伺服器連接埠時"
"生效。"

